metadata.name: M 2 M Flowers
metadata.description:
Flower Pollination 
 
We all have beauty and something special to offer 
The same is true for flowers 
In perfect place and perfect light 
When value is seen and love received  
Like us, he flower blooms. 
We all know that there are many perceptions of beauty 
And many forms of love 
We are like the flower.  
Communicating to each other individual beauty 
The value of the love of flowers 
In nature, same or different, 
Is pollinated by a sharing of feeling.
